Buzzboy/Roboy Red/Major Damage Triple-Frosted Fun Comics

description: Sky-Dog Press joins the 2007 FCBD celebration with 2 all-new, fun and fantastic tales for kids of all ages-- plus comic how-to's and a create your own hero contest! Buzzboy is a milkshake drinking, cheeseburger chomping, super sidekick! Roboy Red is a runaway robot with a heart of gold-- a thermonuclear powered mechanical mite! This special zero issue presents the untold origins of both Buzzboy & Roboy , and is a great way to introduce young readers to the magic of comics.
name: FCBD
